node.text:
During my isolation it was tough not being able to gym, but had to find the motivation to get some type of sweat in so I came up with a few workouts, so here’s a good one! try this if you’re stuck in the house or if your gym isn’t open!

-30 sec jump rope
-30 sec in and out squat jumps
-30 sec RDL to squat
-30 sec lunge up jumps
-30 sec alt side plank twists

Wearing my own @get_tighterr sweat belt to make me feel tight and to sweat a little extra durning my HIIT workouts 😁 you can pre order yours with the link in my bio! 
Sizes S-XXL (true to size)
I’m wearing a medium

node.text:
You guys I’m OBSESSED with this dessert..
Literally every night I make this and eat it after dinner.
Here’s my little tutorial on how I make it!
- 3 egg whites
- 1 scoop @iammotiv8 dessert protein
- 2 TBS coca powder
- 1/2 cup plain pumpkin.
- dash baking powder 
Mix all together and bake on parchment paper for 15-20 min on 350 degrees.
Brownie by it’s self is around d 200 cal and it’s a pretty big size!

If you try this recipe let me know!!
————-
If you want to try this protein use my code MOTIV8JESSICA for free shipping!
This is cookie dough protein, their blueberry is also amazingggg.

node.text:
Goal? TO BE STRONG, FEEL STRONG, AND LOOK STRONG !! 

The other day I hit a PR on deadlift of 185 lbs, (thanks to @katlinalexa_ for the push) was only able to pull it up 2x. Today I was able to pull it up 4 times 😁

Hitting a goal only makes me more motivated to see the next level I can do. Always stay hungry for those goals!!! 🤘🏽🤞🏽

Pre workout - @iammotiv8
Code MOTIV8JESSICA will get you free shipping!
Fav flavor: cherry lemonade 
(Tingle free)

node.text:
You can complain and procrastinate all you want but at the end of the day, you gotta be stronger than the voices in your head, make moves and keep pushing 🤘🏽

Outfit from @buffbunny_collection !
Getfitwjessica = support 🤗

node.text:
I went from knowing absolutely NOTHING about a healthy lifestyle to now sharing what has helped me get through the last 5 years and being where I am today☺️

I’m no where near a professional but I’ve been through one heck of a journey, keeping this mindset positive and I get so excited to help and push others along on their journey!

If you’re looking for a boot camp, the gym I train at is having a special promo where you can get 1 free month of classes when you DM or CALL and mention GETFITWJESSICA. @thebarfittampa 😊

✨Legs abs booty transformation at it’s finest ✨

Deadlifting 60lbs to my PR today of 185lbs 🤘🏽

Change the mindset, it’ll take you places you’d never thought you’d be. Never settle, always keep striving to be the best you can be🔑

node.text:
@realgoodfoods AND AIR FRYER GIVEAWAY‼️‼️

This is a big one you guys😁

I’m picking 1 winner to win a mixed box of @realgoodfoods new and improved bowls AND the winner will also receive an AIR FRYER!!

To enter:
- follow @realgoodfoods and myself.
- like this post
- tag 3 foodie friends
* re share to story for double entry!

You can find these bowls and Walmart, target, Publix and Kroger!

(Must be in the US to enter)
